  <brief_title>Comparison Between Melatonin and Diazepam for Prevention of Recurrent Simple Febrile Seizures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between Melatonin and Diazepam for Prevention of Recurrent Simple Febrile Seizures: Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
