  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of oral melatonin compared to oral diazepam for prevention of
      recurrent simple febrile seizures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy of oral melatonin compared to oral diazepam for prevention of
      recurrence of simple febrile seizures in children aged 6 months to 5 years.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
